      <title>参议院报告称亚马逊忽视了自己的工人安全研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/amazon-ignored-its-own-worker-safety-studies-senate-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据国会委员会的报告，亚马逊公司领导层拒绝了公司放宽仓库工人生产率以减少伤害的内部建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/amazon-ignored-its-own-worker-safety-studies-senate-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:05:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
